{"tid":602074,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"足球史上最震撼登場秀","createTime":"2018-03-22T17:36:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-23T22:15:46.000Z","uid":170369,"like":24,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"1e1d91342aa770addb39b98dd88884c69a3c27f1","tid":602074,"uid":170369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T17:36:31.000Z","msg":"足球史上最震撼登場秀<br />\n<br />\n    2003 年夏天, 水深火熱中的巴塞隆納買來球星朗拿甸奴來救亡 , 並希望於第二輪西甲對陣西維爾的賽事派上這巨星作為登場秀 (Debut show)。不幸地撞上了國際賽期, 朗拿甸奴要於星期三回巴西作賽, 於是巴塞便向西維爾提出把比賽調早一日的請求。西維爾當然不想朗拿甸奴上陣, 斷然拒絕了要求,堅持在週三作賽。<br />\n    最後, 巴塞隆納把球賽時間定成週三凌晨 12時05分進行, 讓朗拿甸奴能上陣後才回巴西。 由於下一天是上班日, 巴塞隆納擔心這場深夜舉行的主場戰, 兼朗拿甸奴的首場賽事會變得極冷清，失去了本來要為增加球隊士氣的原意。 於是便在晚上於 魯營球場舉辦了盛大的嘉年華，包括食物,野餐和音樂表演。 <br />\n<img src=\"https://www.dreamteamfc.com/c/wp-content/uploads/sites/4/2017/05/ronaldinho3.jpg?strip=all&amp;quality=100&amp;w=750\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dreamteamfc.com%2Fc%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fsites%2F4%2F2017%2F05%2Fronaldinho3.jpg%3Fstrip%3Dall%26quality%3D100%26w%3D750&h=135eaa1f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n   凌晨12點， 超過八萬名主場觀眾入場觀看了這場有今生冇來世的比賽。片中 出現了的包括了多名巴塞傳奇: 新加盟的朗拿甸奴,19歲的恩尼斯達,沙維, 域陀華迪斯 時任隊長安歷基 ，座上客哥迪奧拿 ，以及還在西維爾效力的丹尼爾艾維斯。 朗拿甸奴 於比賽後半段寫入世界波 ，為巴塞追平1比1。<br />\n    And the rest is history.<br />\n<br />\n球賽片段:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bS1cPmJXzgE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DbS1cPmJXzgE&d=BIfqzdE3o7%2BAwe8XhhNjbAHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=b5efddd1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bS1cPmJXzgE</a><br />\n<br />\n新聞報導:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.dreamteamfc.com/c/news-gossip/198544/ronaldinho-barcelona-debut-midnight/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dreamteamfc.com%2Fc%2Fnews-gossip%2F198544%2Fronaldinho-barcelona-debut-midnight%2F&d=BIfqzdE3o7%2BAwe8XhhNjbAHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=30eade7f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.dreamteamfc.com/c/news-gossip/198544/ronaldinho-barcelona-debut-midnight/</a>"},{"pid":"966ba18653bfc1be744a028468eafa9390794de7","tid":602074,"uid":24455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T18:03:52.000Z","msg":"隊長咁廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb115bde388733558a9c37dd359e306ccb1597f5","tid":602074,"uid":136901,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T18:11:23.000Z","msg":"又係閪維爾"},{"pid":"65e5cae0963d27bcbd51292a60af7e684618bae1","tid":602074,"uid":170369,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T18:19:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>隊長咁廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n最後睇到丹尼爾先好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5a3df775b42e810e581430f822ae37537539429","tid":602074,"uid":170369,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T18:25:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>又係閪維爾</blockquote><br />\n西維爾唔肯調期都合理嘅😂 估唔到巴塞會絕到凌晨 12 點開波姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5bada8f70f898f5e2aee5237068d637640db79e","tid":602074,"uid":10733,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T18:42:30.000Z","msg":"凌晨都咁鬼好氣好力跑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e37491f482d8cb1e0a53fe84fa24ae0b5c93376e","tid":602074,"uid":7638,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"quote":{"pid":"e5bada8f70f898f5e2aee5237068d637640db79e","tid":602074,"uid":10733,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T18:42:30.000Z","msg":"凌晨都咁鬼好氣好力跑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T19:00:30.000Z","msg":"呢次真係班外國人凌晨踢波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7dbfb32955f8958ff0e468eb671c87bd269dab97","tid":602074,"uid":27251,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T19:21:06.000Z","msg":"好撚痴線 咁多人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad8d009acdfff2c4f880cbec8ed07880ba1df73b","tid":602074,"uid":15984,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T19:27:30.000Z","msg":"2003 年夏天巴塞隆納有幾水深火熱"},{"pid":"8c8665d46fecdd09d1771c149479c6a27f3ad5dd","tid":602074,"uid":49859,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T19:42:15.000Z","msg":"丹狗醒啊，細哨時代俾佢撚左咁多年<br />\n一到美欺時代就轉去疤幫美欺手<br />\n輕鬆呃左個最佳右閘黎做<br />\n難為佢當年西維爾隊友年年國家打比俾人撚狗撚足一個生肖循環<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d6a6f8fa5caa5a203f8e3c4dc9410afc1bf3b1c","tid":602074,"uid":170369,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T20:03:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>2003 年夏天巴塞隆納有幾水深火熱</blockquote><br />\n上一季排第6, 季中甚至跌過落15"},{"pid":"fb7481d724dca76ae00199b5aaccc33a0afcad51","tid":602074,"uid":170369,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T20:07:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>凌晨都咁鬼好氣好力跑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>呢次真係班外國人凌晨踢波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n對朗甸冇問題， 平時嗰個時候落緊club <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63b4bc851bcc408b3cf81e8fa7abc1513adbec59","tid":602074,"uid":4004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T20:10:38.000Z","msg":"正常球員會眼訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c99db33d2402fa1f317e604eb1c6eb9f0735cdf","tid":602074,"uid":170369,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T20:10:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好撚痴線 咁多人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n睇篇英文新聞話當年為左搞好朗甸個presentation ，驚半夜冇人來睇波，派左十萬包kit Kat , 2萬5 包 Doritos <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4972846ff1ae82b0950739b2e7343f50b92771d","tid":602074,"uid":170369,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T20:12:16.000Z","msg":"但我估應該冇一個入場球迷會後悔睇呢場波，係一個王朝嘅開始"},{"pid":"9e8079c9dd38070bb391278f71cd75e695021a0a","tid":602074,"uid":170369,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T11:17:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b6a12f95e786eba77135c6e25b9566b5e2d0bbb","tid":602074,"uid":87072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T11:46:55.000Z","msg":"無人講第一球俾球證黑左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c47889509728311ba3648be67d1aea5eda2d55df","tid":602074,"uid":31215,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T11:49:49.000Z","msg":"最震撼收尾秀應該係美斯魯營告別賽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ad0b81de4aa067267ad532e0116ba183aa4f55d","tid":602074,"uid":170369,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T22:13:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最震撼收尾秀應該係美斯魯營告別賽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係，唔敢想像<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2af3873ab5886d2ed22769d3c55f95f0f7752a38","tid":602074,"uid":170369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T22:15:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最震撼收尾秀應該係美斯魯營告別賽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n朗拿甸奴之後有美斯接棒，但之後應該真係後無來者啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  因為兩個實在太iconic"}]}